Real Madrid, Schalke Advance to Semifinals of Soccer's Champions League

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-04-13T20:36:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/real-madrid-schalke-advance-to-semifinals-of-soccer-s-champions-league.html
Real Madrid beat Tottenham 1-0 to
advance to the Champions League soccer semifinals, while Schalke
defeated Inter Milan 2-1 to eliminate the defending champ.  Cristiano Ronaldo’s goal at White Hart Lane in  London  gave
Real Madrid a 5-0 victory over the two-game quarterfinal. Nine-
time European champion Real will meet archrival Barcelona in the
semifinals.  Raul Gonzalez  and Benedikt Howedes scored as Schalke ended
Inter Milan’s reign by a 7-3 overall score. Schalke will face
 Manchester United  in the last four.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  